{"tid":2517034,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"連續7場淘汰賽遇球荒！卡比路：尼馬無法做領袖","createTime":"2021-05-05T05:12:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T06:21:13.000Z","uid":237459,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6d38df2a2ffb73763307fd3591901e79d21fc07e","tid":2517034,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:12:22.000Z","msg":"賽前稱要戰死球場的尼馬，最終換來巴黎全場0射正遭雙殺出局的結果。卡比路（Fabio Capello）點評說，尼馬（Neymar）不是場上領袖。<br />\n<br />\n上季16強次回合主場對陣多蒙特之後，尼馬已經連續7場歐聯淘汰賽未能入球，卡比路對他的表現感到失望：「我希望他能做點什麼，希望他能更果斷、更有決心。<br />\n<br />\n　　「他嘗試了太多無用的帶球，沒有扮演領袖角色。領袖能夠帶領全隊取得需要的結果，而他說得太多了。」<br />\n　　（馬舸）"},{"pid":"1c44a0b77a6d07862b34163273eaa86c9c6b410b","tid":2517034,"uid":151357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T06:06:27.000Z","msg":"好多年冇睇波 一直講緊果個馬球王 係咪馬列斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e121d3d7ec26e82e18df6bd630356773a8e195","tid":2517034,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c44a0b77a6d07862b34163273eaa86c9c6b410b","tid":2517034,"uid":151357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T06:06:27.000Z","msg":"好多年冇睇波 一直講緊果個馬球王 係咪馬列斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T06:16:16.000Z","msg":"係我地曼聯嘅馬屎眼"},{"pid":"69725d1b3814c482995f1b5da3114fa36134518a","tid":2517034,"uid":186292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70e121d3d7ec26e82e18df6bd630356773a8e195","tid":2517034,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c44a0b77a6d07862b34163273eaa86c9c6b410b","tid":2517034,"uid":151357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T06:06:27.000Z","msg":"好多年冇睇波 一直講緊果個馬球王 係咪馬列斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":